## ISR Track Integration & Tracker Data Relay Module

**Document Version:** 2.1  
**Contract:** FA8802-25-D-0034  
**Classification:** SECRET // NOFORN  
**Date:** 2025-01-15  
**Author:** Technical Architecture Team

---

## 1. Executive Summary

This specification documents the technical changes required to integrate ISR drone tracks into the Joint Logistics Drone deconfliction system and implement a tracker-data relay capability for the intelligence squadron. These changes support mixed-mission airspace operations at three forward operating bases.

**Scope Changes:**
- Add ISR track subscription and ingestion
- Update deconfliction engine for multi-mission airspace
- Implement passive sensor relay module for ISR target data

---

