### 5.2 Recommendation Engine Integration API
**Endpoint:** `POST /external/recommendation/signal`  
**Description:** Pushes throttling signals to platform ranking services.  
**Security:** Mutual TLS (mTLS) + HMAC Signature.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "signals": [
    {
      "content_id": "uuid",
      "weight_modifier": 0.1,
      "reason_code": "TS_INTEGRITY_LOW
